{
  "title": "Tangy Crispy Indian Soybean Croquettes",
  "description": "A midnightcraving Frenchstyle croquette infused with zesty Indian tadka, packed with proteinrich soybeans and dairyfree, crispy coating.",
  "cuisine": "Indian-French fusion",
